WEBVTT

00:10:25.747 --> 00:10:30.109
They offer a chance to reintroduce
native plants and animals to a region.

00:10:30.922 --> 00:10:32.895
They offer public trails,

00:10:32.919 --> 00:10:34.967
places for spiritual practice,

00:10:34.991 --> 00:10:38.106
places for classes and events --

00:10:38.130 --> 00:10:41.282
places where nature and mourning meet.

00:10:42.451 --> 00:10:45.847
Most importantly,
they offer us, once again,

00:10:45.871 --> 00:10:50.998
a chance to just decompose
in a hole in the ground.

00:10:51.966 --> 00:10:53.355
The soil,

00:10:53.379 --> 00:10:55.047
let me tell you,

00:10:55.071 --> 00:10:56.600
has missed us.

00:10:57.155 --> 00:10:59.187
I think for a lot of people,

00:10:59.211 --> 00:11:00.808
they're starting to get the sense